com.example.zoomwroom.Entities

类 DriveRequest.Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.zoomwroom.Entities.DriveRequest.Status
  • 封闭类:
    DriveRequest

    public static final class DriveRequest.Status
extends java.lang.Object
    Status values: PENDING Indicate that the request has been posted and waiting for a driver to accept. ACCEPTED Indicate that the request is accepted by a driver and the driver is waiting for the rider to confirm. CONFIRMED Indicate that the rider has confirmed the ride and waiting for being picked up. ONGOING Indicate that the driver has picked up the rider and is driving to the destination. COMPLETED Indicate that this request is finished. CANCELLED Indicate that the rider canceled this request before any driver accepts it. ABORTED Indicate that the rider has already started his/her riding but want to stop this riding.
    另请参阅:
    Status Description
